Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.25,0:00:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地來沖繩 光顧著玩好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 我們主根源存在本身就已經能起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能如此迅速準備這麼多主根源
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是你的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是為了計劃的實施
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡了自己的那份力罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚要讓主根源們和元神靈訂契約的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏木 要和我訂契約嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種人 實在消受不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:01:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑 等我 我馬上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:28.33,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみが宿った眼に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:28.33,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我悲傷的瞳孔中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:30.69,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映しだす　君のmotion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:30.69,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映出了你閃動的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:34.83,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思いが流れてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:34.83,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思憶潮水般湧來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:38.21,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求められ選択した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:38.21,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我選擇了他們想要的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.76,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その答えは　そうfusion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.76,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可在這選擇的作用下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:44.76,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛みが導く先にある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:44.76,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現的卻是痛苦的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:50.04,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黒い闇　迫っても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:50.04,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是在黑暗面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:55.00,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑顔をいつもくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:55.00,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容始終依舊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:02:00.19,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光を護るため
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:02:00.19,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了守衛光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:07.21,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君と今　ひとつになれる…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:07.21,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我此刻與你融為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:13.04,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追いつけないほどの力　手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:13.04,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得讓人望塵莫及的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:17.56,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風を切って貫いてゆけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:17.56,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後去穿透烈風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:22.70,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰を信じてる…？　通じ合えたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:22.70,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能相互信任理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:27.56,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡起こせる　何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:27.56,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能不斷創造奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:33.48,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真実いつか　見えるから…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:33.48,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能最終發現真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:49.50,i,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 10 「末路」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了 蒔菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:02:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我 比瑢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑大人的汗 有股蜜糖般的香甜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒野也得有個度 黑大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏和清凈之地不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的侍衛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真大人 巫女大人都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起玩吧 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想玩你就自己一個人玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑吧 小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜 聯系上慶太了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑也不在 到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去救覺馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去那邊找找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺馬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 那時的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來打靈石的主意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逼問我聖域的鑰匙在哪也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸突然被你們殺了 還沒來得及跟我說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真活該
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你真的什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經得到鑰匙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞎說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖域的鑰匙 就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人我去接 你去找另外兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有能用滅牙得救世的間隙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 我就要先撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要制造間隙讓小黑用超越技
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用得出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算玩到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很偶然 但我曾發動過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回想起那時的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來啊 出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑大人的對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很吃驚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股容量是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑大人是第一次看我同步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越技也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越技 魔流鬥雫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有用滅牙得救世碰碰運氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的超越技很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再讓你開心點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這眼神真不錯 黑大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍在吸容量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸容量…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類怎麼可能吸人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她並不是主根源 而是負根源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負根源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依據由根源和兩名填補者分攤運的三位一在系統
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過由相遇導致的填補者的死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根源會吸收其容量 成為主根源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼而獲得強大的運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如果顛覆這個原理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人為地留下一個填補者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他所吸收的容量便會轉為負性的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使他成為負根源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負根源 那就是說本來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一樣是填補者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但通過殺掉根源作為負根源重生了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺了根源
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉根源便能逃離填補者的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比瑢答應我和他訂契約便幫我找根源
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每日都在對同步造成消耗的恐懼中度過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根源終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是我殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了成為負根源
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪也找不到 慶太他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒回來 可能跟警察說說會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是佐野茜小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是魁音寺財團的藏木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魁音寺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來接您了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 伊吹也在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉填補者和根源使我獲得了新生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成為了能夠奪取容量和運的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然把媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負根源能從他人處吸取容量填補同步的消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是不死的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然因為這樣的理由殺害慶太的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒同步的黑大人什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 讓我們忘了那只猴子好好玩樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的超越技魔流鬥雫能操縱並轉變水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 能讓體液固化並爆裂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧 我的超越技
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們再多玩一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不怕弄臟手 便能自己改變命運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從小就沒經歷過什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 連小小的幸福都得不到就要死去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想改變命運嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知三位一在系統後我很震驚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有跟我長得一樣的人過著幸福的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能因為我的死而得到容量變得更加幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 把運和容量都搶過來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要改變一出生便已註定了的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是填補者應該能理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你遇見根源也會殺了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點頭就放你一馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也求比瑢讓你成為負根源吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的雙手改變命運獲得幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 真的因此而滿足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得幸福了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我獲得了容量和運 活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒看出你顯得有多幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己也明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是真正的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說 我好不容易才得到了幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要這樣的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 你這個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑 同步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我好好玩玩吧 黑大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑你那稀薄的容量 能有什麼作為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同步的質量都那麼差
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填補者什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也只有試試看了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.81,0:17:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就不用成為負根源這麼邪惡的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太的媽媽也就不會死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連超越技都使不出的你又能做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 打我吧 黑大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的個人喜好而損失重要親人的悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己來體會一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:18:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠體驗黑大人擠出來的這點貴重的容量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在榮幸之至
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越技 滅牙得救世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼把容量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著把不多的容量集中傳送給了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效果還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時候學會的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在使用Thousand的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到自己能一定程度地操縱容量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒能獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是填補者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然填補者無論如何努力也無法幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是壞人 只是想獲得幸福罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:20:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填補者要活下去 只有負根源一條路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當因為沒走這條路而面臨死亡時 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要有三位一在這種系統
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來 再來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來接你了 伊吹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好朋友的樣子也不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:21:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐野小姐已經去我的別墅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤村
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:29.29,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつしか朝を迎え
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:29.29,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺已至清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:34.39,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凍てつく躰溶けて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:34.39,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵硬的身體開始恢復溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:40.51,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覚めた記憶で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:40.51,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我整理思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:46.24,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早すぎた死を還して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:46.24,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕了再度襲來的睡意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:52.23,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲たちの鳴く聲も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:52.23,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲兒低鳴的聲音消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:58.24,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥たちの舞う羽音にも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:58.24,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥兒展翅的聲音也沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:04.24,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音を亡くした　白き涸れ地に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:04.24,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬籟俱靜　一片慘白的荒蕪大地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,0:22:10.34,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あふれる彩を　そそいでいく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,0:22:10.34,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地被陽光染上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.38,0:22:14.11,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あざやかに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.38,0:22:14.11,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絢麗的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.55,0:22:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.87,0:22:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了不少貢獻啊 比瑢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小子難道要把我的容量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為猴子能駕馭得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的元神靈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 藏木 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.56,0:22:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你高貴的容量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:52.29,o,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode 「重逢」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給我這只下等猴子使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.84,0:22:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:22:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 別吸取我的容量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.31,0:23:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你不要吸了嗎
